flowchart TD

A[Start] --> B[Power ON ESP32<br>Initialize Sensors & LCD]

B --> C[Read Temperature Sensor]
C --> D[Read Current Sensor]
D --> E[Check Load Status (ON/OFF)]

E --> F{Overload or<br>Overheating?}

F -- Yes --> G[Trigger Auto Cut-Off]
G --> H[Display Alert on LCD]
H --> I[Log Fault Event]
I --> J[Stop]

F -- No --> K[Update Working Time Counter]
K --> L[Display Runtime, Current & Temperature on LCD]
L --> M{User Turns OFF Load?}

M -- Yes --> N[Stop Timer<br>Save Runtime Log]
N --> J[Stop]

M -- No --> C[Continue Monitoring]

J --> O[End]
